2B08BF42.Line7.AFA94: Do what I should have done from the start... toss it in the fire and turn it to ash.

5D2B52BC.Line1.AFA94: I found it when I was cataloging an old tomb. It said my family would never be hungry again.

C4FD38C4.Line9.AFA94: (sigh) I knew it would find its way back to me somehow...

F71FCC3E.Line3.AFA94: But I... now I owe it my soul. So I hid it, and tried to forget about it. Looks like it found itself another willing debtor after me...
